HyDE Gallery curated theme assets
=================================

This directory integrates ONE pinned HyDE Gallery theme declaratively. The
theme is fetched as a flake input pinned by commit (see flake.nix input
`hyde-theme-catppuccin-mocha`). Only allowlisted color fields are parsed; no
theme scripts (*.theme, *.dcol, justfile, theme.patch.sh, wallbash) are sourced
or executed, and nothing is written to ~/.config/hyde.

This is NOT full HyDE Gallery support. See "Compatibility scope" below.

