Wallpapers
----------
Configs/.config/hyde/themes/Catppuccin Mocha/wallpapers/* are provided as
read-only store assets and attached to the existing wallpaper domain search
path. They are NOT copied into $HOME. NO license is claimed for these
wallpapers: their authorship and licensing are unverified. Do not redistribute
without independently confirming their license.

Update procedure
----------------
1. git ls-remote https://github.com/HyDE-Project/hyde-themes refs/heads/Catppuccin-Mocha
2. Update the rev in flake.nix input `hyde-theme-catppuccin-mocha`.
3. nix flake lock --update-input hyde-theme-catppuccin-mocha
4. Re-verify archive folder names AND re-check for any LICENSE files; update
   this NOTICE (do not upgrade "UNVERIFIED" to a concrete license without a
   verifiable source in the pinned artifact).

Compatibility scope
-------------------
Supported here: this single curated, declarative palette + assets adapter.
NOT supported: hydectl theme switching, hyde-shell, wallbash runtime color
extraction, theme.patch.sh, and any mutable GTK/Qt patching. Theme switching is
done by changing vars.theme and rebuilding.
